Vulois

Vulois looked at Optimus

"Good good. That means she is on her way to talkng to the Maximals. I 
just don't know what Cybershark is up to.(Vulois than sees Child come 
up in the corner of his eye.) Oh! Excuse me Optimus, but I'm going to 
have to ask you to leave now. I have a studetn waiting to be trained."

Brix/Fliq

Brix and Fliq walked into the bridge of their old ship, so stunned at 
seeing all their old history to bother looking at Ramulus. They 
headed over to the main computer.

"Well, here it is. Ramulus, I'm sure you know how to remove a 
computer. You can show us how without destroying it. Ramulus? 
Ramulus? Oh Man! He didn't follow us! He could get lost in the ship. 
Go find him Fliq."


Starscream

Starscream looked at Megatron, and realized that he was the Megatron 
from the Beast Wars. Maybe their still was a chance of being accepted 
into the Predacons. He bowed before Megatron.

"Megatron, I ask to be enrolled into your service. I no longer crave 
power, only destruction. My record speaks for itself, as I have won 
every battle in my life except for Galvatron. Please Megatron, allow 
me to be your warrior."


Fliq ran out of the bridge and began looking for Ramulus.

"Ramulus! Hey, where are you buddy?"
